<br>
The new TLC rule doesn't change much of anything for FD'ers -- just means Bjond will have to FD it over to the lower folks for the kill (eg. monk PL style kills).  Non-FD'ers can always hurt him bad and then /q (or better, root and /camp if you or lower can root) -- just make sure you don't hurt them into flee-mode.<br>
<br>
IMHO, TLC is just pain-in-the-ass code.  It doesn't stop you if you really want something and doesn't block farming.  It does make questing, especially step-wise questing, much more difficult, though.  Ah well, thanks for the tip on TLC.  It would have been painful to discover the new rules the hard way on a particular long/rare spawn camp. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1>Firiona Vie General Chat</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.9.5.3<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

